⚙️ 2. STEP 1 — AWS BACKEND (SANGAT PENTING)

Di main.tf:

terraform {
  required_version = ">= 1.5"

  required_providers {
    aws = {
      source  = "hashicorp/aws"
      version = "~> 5.0"
    }
  }

  backend "s3" {
    bucket         = "lks2026-tfstate"
    key            = "infra/terraform.tfstate"
    region         = "ap-southeast-3"
    dynamodb_table = "lks2026-tf-lock"
    encrypt        = true
  }
}
⚠️ WAJIB dibuat dulu di AWS:

Sebelum terraform init, kamu harus bikin:

1. S3 Bucket
lks2026-tfstate
2. DynamoDB Table (lock state)
Table name: lks2026-tf-lock
Partition key: LockID (String)
🌐 3. STEP 2 — PROVIDER AWS

Masih di main.tf:

provider "aws" {
  region = var.aws_region

  default_tags {
    tags = {
      Project     = "LKS2026"
      Environment = "Production"
      ManagedBy   = "Terraform"
    }
  }
}
🧩 4. STEP 3 — VARIABLES

variables.tf

