🌍 5. STEP 4 — VPC (SUDAH BENAR TAPI ADA TAMBAHAN PENTING)

Yang kamu punya sudah bagus.

TAPI kurang ini:

➜ Route Table wajib

Tambahkan:

resource "aws_route_table" "public" {
  vpc_id = aws_vpc.main.id

  route {
    cidr_block = "0.0.0.0/0"
    gateway_id = aws_internet_gateway.main.id
  }
}

resource "aws_route_table_association" "public" {
  count          = length(aws_subnet.public)
  subnet_id      = aws_subnet.public[count.index].id
  route_table_id = aws_route_table.public.id
}
🔐 6. SECURITY (WAJIB UNTUK ECS + ALB)

security.tf

resource "aws_security_group" "alb_sg" {
  vpc_id = aws_vpc.main.id

  ingress {
    from_port   = 80
    to_port     = 80
    protocol    = "tcp"
    cidr_blocks = ["0.0.0.0/0"]
  }

  egress {
    from_port   = 0
    to_port     = 0
    protocol    = "-1"
    cidr_blocks = ["0.0.0.0/0"]
  }
}
📦 7. PERINTAH JALAN (URUTAN BENAR)

Jalankan ini:

terraform init

Kalau error:

cek AWS credential
cek region S3 bucket
terraform fmt -recursive
terraform validate
terraform plan -out=tfplan
terraform apply tfplan
🚨 ERROR YANG PALING SERING TERJADI
❌ 1. ExpiredToken

➡️ AWS login sudah expired

✔ Solusi:

aws configure
❌ 2. S3 bucket not found

➡️ backend belum dibuat

✔ Solusi:
buat manual di AWS console

❌ 3. DynamoDB lock error

➡️ table belum ada

❌ 4. Region mismatch

➡️ S3 beda region dengan terraform

